1
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,319
You come to me

2
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:11,400
because the new factory plan failed.

3
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,560
You want to come back to me, huh?

4
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:17,719
You didn't look like this

5
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,680
when you got into my car.

6
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,560
A man should be adaptable.

7
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,239
Now you should know

8
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,200
on the Black Rock Island,

9
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,359
I'm the only one

10
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,959
who doesn't listen to the Lu guy.

11
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,680
And,

12
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,120
my people are responsible

13
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,840
the

14
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:37,040
raw material processing,

15
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:38,640
while you

16
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:42,359
are only responsible for transportation and distribution,

17
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,760
yet take the lion's share of the profits.

18
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:45,439
Isn't that unfair?

19
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:50,159
So you took the opportunity to trade collectibles

20
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,719
and made a fortune.

21
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,040
Everyone takes what they need.

22
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,599
And,

23
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,079
from now on,

24
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,480
the profit share will be adjusted.

25
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,280
After all, I have to

26
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,359
deal with that Lu guy.

27
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,120
All these years,

28
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,719
have you never investigated

29
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,039
Lu Zhiyu's background?

30
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:11,280
I can't find anything.

31
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,599
Get me a drug with theobromine,

32
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,360
colorless and tasteless.

33
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,080
Young Master Xie,

34
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,759
are you feeling unwell?

35
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,120
No.

36
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,680
My dog's been disobedient.

37
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,360
I need to make it behave.

38
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,240
Ready.

39
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,560
Go.

40
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,039
I didn't expect you to

41
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,599
be having arm wrestling competition

42
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,840
instead of being on guard on the Night of the Full Moon.

43
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,080
The power of the tide

44
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,360
will make our adrenaline surge.

45
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,439
Whether it's strength, speed,

46
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:08,960
or the desire to win,

47
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,800
it will all be more intense

48
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,039
than usual.

49
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,759
One more time.

50
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,520
Bro.

51
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:20,120
The sentry found

52
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,400
Qin Yaxin,

53
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,879
who ran away from home,

54
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,800
appeared in the nearby woods.

55
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,159
You ask Zhang San and Li Si

56
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,199
to drive her away.

57
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:28,680
I'll go.

58
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,000
I'll go.

59
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,360
A bunch of followers.

60
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,599
So annoying.

61
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,879
You dig the hole, you jump in.

62
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,160
A Che.

63
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,759
Pull me up.

64
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,000
If you don't ask me this time,

65
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,519
I won't pull you up.

66
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,839
I was loyal last time.

67
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:32,839
I didn't betray you.

68
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,160
You not only don't appreciate me,

69
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,199
but laugh at me.

70
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,000
Is that fair?

71
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,279
The person who failed in the negotiation

72
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,600
has no right to talk about fairness.

73
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,279
And you didn't take Jiang Yue away,

74
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,560
and got my brother involved.

75
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,839
This is your punishment.

76
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,839
There's a snake!

77
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,279
Help!

78
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,279
It's coming!

79
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,800
Help me, A Che!

80
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,199
Pull me up!

81
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,600
It bit me!

82
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,199
Have you heard of the story of the wolf?

83
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,040
Can you leave me here to feed the wolf?

84
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,600
Are there really wolves here at night?

85
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:15,399
This lousy forest

86
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,079
is so confusing.

87
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,079
I can lead you out.

88
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,480
You're just as grumpy

89
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,759
as your brother.

90
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,519
But you're

91
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,279
a bit more human.

92
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,519
Shut up or you'll feed the snakes.

93
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:34,879
Look at you.

94
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,480
Either you care about your brother

95
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,480
and can't stand hearing anything bad about him,

96
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:40,600
or

97
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:42,759
you hate being praised for being kind.

98
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,000
They ran away.

99
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,160
They must be sent by my dad.

100
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,800
They want to take me home.

101
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,480
Seeing that I have help,

102
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,879
they gave up.

103
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,399
You have family, but you don't go home.

104
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,240
You don't know how lucky you are.

105
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:08,879
You don't know.

106
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,920
My dad wants to arrange for me

107
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,759
to get engaged to the leader of another gang.

108
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,680
Even if I can't get the man I want,

109
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,399
I can't be forced to marry

110
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,040
a man I don't know at all.

111
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,920
How about you be my boyfriend?

112
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,439
Don't be nervous.

113
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,600
I just hire you to play a role.

114
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,279
The reward is up to you.

115
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,399
You

116
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:39,240
pretend to be the young master of another gang

117
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,000
and go home with me.

118
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:40,879
I

119
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,600
will tell my dad that I have a boyfriend.

120
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:44,199
Let's see what he can do about it.

121
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:47,120
Don't even think about it.

122
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,839
If you don't agree,

123
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,160
I'll tell the whole world

124
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:54,120
that it was you, A Che, who saved me with your kindness.

125
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:56,120
And you are especially family-oriented.

126
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,639
I thought

127
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:16,319
he would keep you by his side.

128
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:17,759
Brother,

129
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,879
Lu Zhiyu didn't restrict my freedom.

130
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,879
I wanted to stay in the woods

131
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,000
to observe wildlife.

132
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:24,600
Observe what?

133
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,839
Wild wolves?

134
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,480
How do you know?

135
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,319
It seems I'm right.

136
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,480
There are wolves around here.

137
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,920
And some outrageous rumors.

138
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,199
But they're all made up to scare people.

139
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:41,720
Don't lie to me, Moon.

140
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:42,879
You hid from me

141
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:43,920
and our family

142
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,600
that you changed your major and job.

143
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,639
I could tolerate it,

144
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,079
even pretend not to know.

145
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,519
Xie family's children have no freedom.

146
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:51,839
For my own selfish reasons,

147
00:07:52,319 --> 00:07:54,000
I hope you can fulfill all your wishes.

148
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,079
But what you should observe

149
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,360
is real wildlife,

150
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,560
not monsters.

151
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,199
They are not monsters.

152
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:02,480
They are just different from ordinary humans.

153
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,720
Because humans are intolerant of differences,

154
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:06,120
they choose to live in seclusion.

155
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,160
Those people can crush you

156
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,120
and swallow you at any time.

157
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,399
Aren't you afraid?

158
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:12,600
At least I believe he won't hurt me.

159
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,079
That's just naive and stupid.

160
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,399
You can be capricious,

161
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,600
run away from home,

162
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,839
and lie all the time.

163
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,279
But if you leave me,

164
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,120
you'll put yourself in a dangerous situation

165
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,600
where you could die at any moment.

166
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,240
I, Xie Chen, won't allow it.

167
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,879
Who I'm with,

168
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,399
why do I need your permission?

169
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,159
I have the freedom to choose my own life.

170
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:36,000
Go.

171
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:38,039
Now that you know who I am,

172
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,120
you should know

173
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,799
what will happen to you if you make trouble in our territory.

174
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,639
You are not welcome here.

175
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:48,840
Go.

176
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,360
Stupid dog.

177
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,039
I have plenty of ways to bring my sister home.

178
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,320
What do you want me to wear?

179
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,240
You should be imposing, manly,

180
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,759
tall, brave and safe.

181
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,639
You look like a little boy now.

182
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:23,879
How can I let my dad

183
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,440
marry you off to my sister?

184
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,600
Try this one.

185
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,799
You look like my brother now.

186
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,000
You look like a man now.

187
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,759
But I still feel something missing.

188
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,480
Although you are not as good as your brother,

189
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,039
you are still acceptable.

190
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,519
I am me.

191
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,840
My brother is my brother.

192
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:50,240
Why do you always want to dress me up like him?

193
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:51,440
If you like him so much,

194
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,600
why don't you go ask him for help?

195
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,600
Waste of time.

196
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:54,840
Wait.

197
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:55,759
What?

198
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,759
Swipe the card.

199
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:04,960
Actually,

200
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,960
you look pretty handsome when you're not in a good mood.

201
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,000
Remember,

202
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,120
when you see my dad later,

203
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,159
just act like this.

204
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,399
This is my boyfriend,

205
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,159
the Young Master of the Python Gang,

206
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,159
Master Long.

207
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:19,960
Mr. Qin.

208
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:21,320
Nice to meet you.

209
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,080
The Python Gang?

210
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,639
I've never heard of it.

211
00:11:26,159 --> 00:11:28,559
You're always focused on your rivals,

212
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,919
ignoring the outside world

213
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:33,399
and your daughter's feelings.

214
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:35,799
Alright, alright.

215
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,080
The man my daughter likes

216
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:41,159
must be a hero.

217
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,120
But

218
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,360
he looks a bit familiar.

219
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:55,120
A poor delivery guy

220
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,840
wants to marry into the Qin family?

221
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,360
So what if he's poor?

222
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,600
I don't want to be a tool in a business marriage.

223
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:07,039
I just like him.

224
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,240
I love him, and I want to marry him.

225
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:09,279
Let's go.

226
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
Shameless!

227
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:29,200
What you just said

228
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,399
is different from this.

229
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,080
I did go a bit overboard.

230
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,639
But don't worry,

231
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:36,000
I'll give you extra pay.

232
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:42,240
Why is your face so red?

233
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:48,559
Are you feeling feverish?

234
00:12:53,679 --> 00:12:55,440
Are you blushing?

235
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,519
Was that your first kiss?

236
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:07,159
But it was my first kiss too.

237
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,240
I didn't even mind.

238
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,279
Are you crazy?

239
00:13:19,279 --> 00:13:20,600
Do you hate me that much?

240
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,159
Young Master Xie,

241
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,600
I'm giving you a gift.

242
00:13:28,759 --> 00:13:31,679
If you still want to take back the Lighthouse Port,

243
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,480
do it tonight.

244
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,279
Robbery?

245
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:36,080
Yes.

246
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:37,200
Robbery.

247
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,639
Send more people

248
00:13:39,519 --> 00:13:40,639
and make some noise.

249
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,720
After tonight,

250
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,279
you won't have a chance.

251
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:52,399
I suddenly feel so hot now.

252
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,360
I feel like I'm having a fever.

253
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,000
42 degrees.

254
00:13:58,279 --> 00:14:00,759
Now your blood is flowing in my body.

255
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:03,519
Will I become a wolf girl?

256
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:05,639
Then we'll live in the jungle.

257
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,240
Okay.

258
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,200
Hello.

259
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:23,440
Brother.

260
00:14:23,919 --> 00:14:24,399
Something's wrong.

261
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,279
Something big happened.

262
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:28,279
A group of thugs are causing trouble near the harbor.

263
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:30,000
Some fishermen were seriously injured.

264
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,639
The fishing boats were also destroyed.

265
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:33,679
[You should come over quickly.]

266
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,759
Okay, I got it.

267
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,120
Something happened.

268
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,000
There are some thugs

269
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,000
causing trouble near the lighthouse.

270
00:14:44,519 --> 00:14:45,919
Several fishermen were seriously injured,

271
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,120
and fishing boats were destroyed.

272
00:14:47,759 --> 00:14:48,559
I have to go.

273
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:52,159
What if they're targeting you?

274
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:54,960
If they're targeting me,

275
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,360
then I can't just hide at home

276
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,000
and let those innocent people suffer.

277
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:02,559
I'll go with you.

278
00:15:04,039 --> 00:15:05,000
Stay at home.

279
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:06,759
Don't worry.

280
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,159
I'll be back soon.

281
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,039
I won't lose control.
